{"fsPath":"/home/khanh/src/0_github/revcli/docs/ARCHITECTURE.md","fileUuid":"910d3c42-351a-4642-91ea-3b302d313117","fileSizeBytes":11461,"numLines":337,"diffChanges":[{"originalStartLineNumberOneIndexed":1,"originalEndLineNumberExclusiveOneIndexed":1,"modifiedStartLineNumberOneIndexed":1,"modifiedEndLineNumberExclusiveOneIndexed":338,"addedLines":["# Revcli — Architecture","","Terminal-based AI code reviewer (Go 1.25, Cobra CLI, Bubble Tea TUI). This document maps layers, data flow, and major packages. **Code links** open the GitHub file viewer at the exact line range (branch `main`).","","---","","## 1. System context","","```mermaid","flowchart LR","  Dev([\"Developer\"])","  R[\"revcli\\nCLI + TUI\"]","  LLM[\"LLM APIs\\n(OpenAI, Anthropic,\\nGoogle, …)\"]","  MCP[\"MCP servers\"]","  LSP[\"Language servers\\n(LSP)\"]","  FS[\"Git & filesystem\"]","  Dev -->|\"TTY, flags, stdin\"| R","  R --> LLM","  R --> MCP","  R --> LSP","  R --> FS","```","","---","","## 2. Entry points and commands","","```mermaid","flowchart LR","  subgraph entry[\"Process entry\"]","    M[\"main.go\"]","    E[\"cmd.Execute\"]","  end","  subgraph cmds[\"Cobra commands\"]","    R[\"revcli (default)\"]","    RV[\"review\"]","    P[\"preset\"]","    U[\"update-providers\"]","  end","  M --> E","  E --> R","  E --> RV","  E --> P","  E --> U","```","","| Role | Location (clickable) |","|------|----------------------|","| Process entry | [`main.go` L7–9](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/main.go#L7-L9) |","| CLI bootstrap (`fang`, version, signals) | [`internal/cmd/root.go` L109–132](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L109-L132) |","| Default command: setup → Bubble Tea TUI | [`internal/cmd/root.go` L63–90](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L63-L90) |","| Shared app setup (config, DB, `app.New`) | [`internal/cmd/root.go` L157–205](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L157-L205) |","| `review` subcommand | [`internal/cmd/review.go` L26–67](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/review.go#L26-L67) |","","**Modes**","","- **Interactive default (`revcli`)**: [`setupAppWithProgressBar`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L146-L153) → [`tui.New`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L691-L713) → `tea.NewProgram` → [`program.Run`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L77-L88).","- **`revcli review`**: Same [`setupApp`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L157-L205); then either Bubble Tea [`internal/ui`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L35-L99) (interactive) or [`App.RunNonInteractive`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L125-L128).","","---","","## 3. Layered architecture","","```mermaid","flowchart TB","  subgraph presentation[\"Presentation\"]","    TUI[\"internal/tui — main chat TUI\"]","    UI[\"internal/ui — review-focused TUI\"]","    CMD[\"internal/cmd — Cobra\"]","  end","  subgraph application[\"Application\"]","    APP[\"internal/app — wiring, lifecycle, events\"]","    AGT[\"internal/agent — SessionAgent, Coordinator\"]","    PRM[\"internal/permission\"]","  end","  subgraph domain[\"Domain & services\"]","    SES[\"internal/session\"]","    MSG[\"internal/message\"]","    HIS[\"internal/history\"]","    CTX[\"internal/context — review/builder\"]","    PST[\"internal/preset\"]","  end","  subgraph infrastructure[\"Infrastructure\"]","    DB[\"internal/db — sqlc + SQLite\"]","    LSP[\"internal/lsp\"]","    OAUTH[\"internal/oauth/*\"]","    CFG[\"internal/config\"]","    TOOLS[\"internal/agent/tools/*\"]","    MCP[\"internal/agent/tools/mcp\"]","  end","  CMD --> TUI","  CMD --> UI","  CMD --> APP","  TUI --> APP","  UI --> APP","  APP --> AGT","  APP --> SES","  APP --> MSG","  APP --> HIS","  APP --> PRM","  APP --> LSP","  AGT --> SES","  AGT --> MSG","  AGT --> TOOLS","  AGT --> MCP","  SES --> DB","  MSG --> DB","  HIS --> DB","  CFG --> OAUTH","  APP --> CFG","```","","---","","## 4. `App` composition (service container)","","[`internal/app.App`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L43-L63) aggregates persistence, permissions, agent coordination, LSP, and config. Construction in [`app.New`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L65-L118):","","```mermaid","flowchart LR","  N[\"app.New\"] --> S[\"session.Service\"]","  N --> M[\"message.Service\"]","  N --> H[\"history.Service\"]","  N --> P[\"permission.Service\"]","  N --> C[\"agent.Coordinator\"]","  N --> L[\"LSPClients map\"]","  N --> BG[\"initLSPClients / checkForUpdates / mcp.Initialize\"]","```","","Background work started from [`app.New`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L95-L104): LSP client init, update checks, MCP initialization.","","---","","## 5. Agent stack (LLM + tools)","","**Libraries**: [`charm.land/fantasy`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/go.mod) for multi-provider LLM; Catwalk for model metadata; tools implement `fantasy.AgentTool`.","","```mermaid","flowchart TB","  COO[\"agent.Coordinator\"]","  SA[\"SessionAgent (sessionAgent)\"]","  COO --> SA","  SA --> LM[\"large/small Model (fantasy.LanguageModel)\"]","  SA --> T[\"[]fantasy.AgentTool\"]","  T --> BASH[\"bash\"]","  T --> EDIT[\"edit / multiedit / write\"]","  T --> GREP[\"grep / glob\"]","  T --> FETCH[\"fetch / web_fetch\"]","  T --> MCP[\"MCP bridge\"]","  T --> LSPt[\"diagnostics / view\"]","```","","| Component | Code |","|-----------|------|","| Coordinator contract | [`internal/agent/coordinator.go` L44–58](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/coordinator.go#L44-L58) |","| Coordinator construction | [`NewCoordinator`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/coordinator.go#L74-L82) |","| Session agent + queue / cancel | [`internal/agent/agent.go` L62–97](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/agent.go#L62-L97), [`NewSessionAgent`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/agent.go#L112-L120) |","| Tool registration surface | [`internal/agent/tools`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/tree/main/internal/agent/tools) |","","**Config**: Agent kinds such as `reviewer` are defined in [`internal/config/config.go` L63–68](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/config/config.go#L63-L68).","","---","","## 6. Two Bubble Tea UIs","","| UI | Purpose | Root model |","|----|---------|------------|","| **`internal/tui`** | Full product: chat, dialogs, sessions, completions, splash | [`appModel`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L59-L90) via [`tui.New`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L691-L713) |","| **`internal/ui`** | Streamlined review + follow-up chat for `revcli review` | [`ui.Model`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L35-L99) via [`NewModel`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L101-L103) |","","```mermaid","flowchart TB","  subgraph tui_pkg[\"internal/tui\"]","    AM[\"appModel\"]","    PG[\"page/* e.g. chat\"]","    DL[\"components/dialogs/*\"]","    CH[\"components/chat/*\"]","    AM --> PG","    AM --> DL","    PG --> CH","  end","  subgraph ui_pkg[\"internal/ui\"]","    UM[\"Model + state machine\"]","    UM --> VP[\"viewport / textarea / list\"]","  end","```","","[`app.Subscribe(program)`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/root.go#L82-L82) connects app-level events into the main TUI message pump.","","---","","## 7. Persistence (SQLite + sqlc)","","```mermaid","erDiagram","  sessions ||--o{ messages : contains"," 